snippet.title: Everdell Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Harvest resources to build a woodland village in a beloved digital board game!

Adapted from the award-winning board game from Tabletop Tycoon, Everdell is a fantastical city building game combining worker placement and strategic card play to create a new civilization.
